title: PLAZA / WORKING CLASS DRUNK barks
description: Barks from a working class man with a drinking problem. Triggers an authority orb if you've met the working class woman.

dialogueTree.title: Working Class Drunk: ""T's shit ain't nothing to me...""
Working Class Drunk: ""I make my own way, t's all. Always..."
dialogueTree.english: "I make my own way, t's all. Always have, always will."
dialogueTree.polish: „Chodzę swoją drogą i tyle. Zawsze tak było i zawsze będzie”.
dialogueTree.belarusian: "Хаджу сваёй дарогай і ўсё. Заўсёды так было і заўсёды будзе".

dialogueTree.title: Working Class Drunk: ""They don't know me... no one *know..."
dialogueTree.english: "They don't know me... no one *knows* me... (hic)."
dialogueTree.polish: „Oni mnie nie znają... Nikt mnie nie *zna*... Czk...”
dialogueTree.belarusian: "Яны мяне не ведаюць... Ніхто мяне не *ведае*... Ік..."

dialogueTree.title: Working Class Drunk: ""I work hard, I play hard... *Nobod..."
dialogueTree.english: "I work hard, I play hard... *Nobody* works harder!"
dialogueTree.polish: „Pracuję na całego i bawię się na całego... *Nikt* nie pracuje ciężej!”
dialogueTree.belarusian: "Я працую на поўную і гуляю на поўную... *Ніхто* не працуе цяжэй!"

dialogueTree.title: Working Class Drunk: ""I's hard you know... It's j'st so..."
dialogueTree.english: "I's hard you know... It's j'st so hard sometimes... (hic)."
dialogueTree.polish: „Tak trudno... Czasem jest tak trudno... Czk...”
dialogueTree.belarusian: "Так цяжка... Часам бывае так цяжка... Гык..."

dialogueTree.title: Working Class Drunk: ""All I got I built with my bare han..."
dialogueTree.english: "All I got I built with my bare hands..."
dialogueTree.belarusian: "Усё, што я маю, я пабудаваў уласнымі рукамі..."

dialogueTree.title: Working Class Drunk: ""I ain't got shit...""
Working Class Drunk: ""I'm scum, just a scummy ol' scum...""
dialogueTree.english: "I'm scum, just a scummy ol' scum..."

dialogueTree.title: Working Class Drunk: ""I don't deserve 'er, I don't deser..."
dialogueTree.english: "I don't deserve 'er, I don't deserve anybody..."
dialogueTree.polish: „Nie zasługuję na nią. Na nikogo nie zasługuję...”
dialogueTree.belarusian: "Я не заслугоўваю яе. На нікога не заслугоўваю..."
